Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:28.82,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(435,100)\fad(500,500)}「因為千尋來看我了哦！」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓喵…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:46.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}忠海站和竹原站的開頭發音都是「た」（ta）。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為聽到了「た」  我還以為到竹原了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匆匆忙忙下車  結果到了一個叫忠海的站
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我馬上就去坐下一趟電車啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  下一趟要過一小時才來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋你先等著  我去問問媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看有沒有人可以開車去接你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠海？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  離下一趟電車來還有一小時…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.81,0:03:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去接吧  楓你回玉響咖啡店等著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是剛才借的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…媽媽在騎機車
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.23,0:03:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:03:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也有機車？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.05,0:04:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是長大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾位是以前關照過你媽媽的騎手俱樂部的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你出生的時候  我們大家都來看過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼點點大的小寶寶居然長得這麼漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了  是因為上年紀了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近眼睛變得容易流汗了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  想看玉惠以前的照片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉惠姐以前很帥的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體型雖然小  但是機車騎得很熟練呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都已經長得這麼大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.15,0:04:59.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還來邀請我們說「好久沒騎過了  下次的騎行大家一起去吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽和機車
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想坐上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來了  回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經騎得很慢了  還是覺得害怕嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  很開心的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓喵  好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.81,0:05:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待下次的騎行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短信聯繫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天謝謝你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是媽媽讓我帶的土產
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  千尋會由我們來好好照料的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章魚的天婦羅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.62,0:05:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋很喜歡吃章魚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:55.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也吃吃看  吃吃看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:05:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是廣島油菜  我最喜歡吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:06.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  是因為章魚很好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是因為楓喵在平常地笑著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開朗地在生活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.78,0:06:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉呢  覺得安心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋和楓從小學起就一直在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  楓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.76,0:06:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗喲噗喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:55.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神真好呢噗喲助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:57.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又多了很多新夥伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要向小薰她們介紹你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓喵每天都有拍照片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大概是有每天在拍啦  雖然沒什麼長進
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能在竹原見到千尋了  好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:29.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.73,0:07:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音你太緊張了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:45.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪的朋友  我記得是個愛哭鬼吧  薰親
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是個淚腺脆弱的人  還有不要叫我薰親
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得注意別不小心打開她的淚腺開關了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.29,0:07:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都到了  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  多麼閃亮的香親笑容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是要把紀惠親我給萌死嗎  是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:11.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心亂了陣腳  不妙不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.15,0:08:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫三次千尋  這次…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呦  沒想到能在這裡和你相見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是岡崎紀惠  多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是塙薰  請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是櫻田麻音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.19,0:08:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快去吃什錦燒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.36,0:08:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.18,0:08:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就照香親說的  去吃吧去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:09:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是新品「HOBORO燒」  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好聞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  聞起來真香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.82,0:09:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡情地來品嚐以戰勝夏天的暑氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.48,0:09:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香親  很燙的哦  要我幫你吹吹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎  不燙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  就是用這個吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很燙的  要小心吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋是第一次來竹原吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  那你們待會兒得帶她好好四處轉轉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪  等下去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:57.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  那個…我想想從哪兒開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  你先吃完再說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們真的叫你小啪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.95,0:10:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在這裡我被叫做小啪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:15.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是  我家姐姐看到小啪的動作後命名的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊你是怎麼叫的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓喵…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓喵楓喵…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得是剛上小學的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來玩躲避球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我等我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三次千尋同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤渡楓…楓…楓喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.29,0:10:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋和我都不擅長交新朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不正好有個合適的去處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:23.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}竹原本町大道石階旁的名勝。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「舉地藏」？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說一邊許願一邊抱起地藏菩薩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果比想像中的要輕的話  那個願望就能實現哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢  畢竟是石頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當情緒下降的時候  果然還是要吃二重燒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在高處吃的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更能情緒UP！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.76,0:12:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這風景如何啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:17.56,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}這裡是指竹原港方向的竹原冶煉廠的煙囪。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  煙囪那頭還能看到海呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶爾和大家一起來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:22.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個不錯的地方吧  千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜食和美景都沒辦法提升她的情緒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  現在我情緒很高漲的…說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:42.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛  太可愛了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小傢伙是什麼啊  軟綿綿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:03.99,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情緒高漲到爆了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃貓大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃貓大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這感覺真棒  情緒高漲起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣達到最高點吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老姐發信息來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我不敢聽  但是內容是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是絕好的探險之日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不祥的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就無視掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.48,0:13:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  無視什麼的好過分哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經出現了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從哪出現的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:14:02.03,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}竹原市忠海町的山，被當地人愛稱為「黑瀧先生」。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:14:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  大家一起去黑瀧山  讓情緒UP吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.28,0:14:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑瀧山？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開車去嗎  恐怖的駕駛再臨…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走路去？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:17.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  打起精神出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走去黑瀧山…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦  在這種探險的大好日子裡才不要開車呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起佐代美姐的駕駛這還算是好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能這樣想了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓喵  忠海就是我下錯車的那一站嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是很遠嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:43.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}這之後1小時後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:52.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}2小時後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐電車不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一點就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:27.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}3小時後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  休息5分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,0:15:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這裡的話就只有一點了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:42.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶  要吃汽水橡皮糖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.66,0:15:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汽水橡皮糖？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  是紀惠我親手做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不吃那種奇怪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕她就好了  千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚嗚  誰都不吃我做的汽水橡皮糖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不合格
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  香親居然來吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀惠親我的幸福指數一下子就滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.62,0:16:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多吃點  吃多少都行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋自己做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:28.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋喜歡可愛的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口哨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  還有一點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定不止一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.42,0:17:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要繼續走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  已經到了哦  登山口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.98,0:17:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要爬黑瀧山啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才剛開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.68,0:17:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好做準備體操哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備體操2分鐘？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.38,0:17:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  因為到山頂要二三十分鐘嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又囧又可愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手制的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新角色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:33.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好地方呢  楓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.86,0:18:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是第一次來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠和千尋來沒來過的地方  真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:19:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓喵過得很好  很好  真的過得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋  謝謝你為我擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來淚腺的開關在那裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現小香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.99,0:19:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交朋友可真不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.12,0:19:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不擅長交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有被誰搭話的經歷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.79,0:19:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在同班有個對噗喲助…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:47.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這孩子叫噗喲助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說這孩子很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.22,0:19:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.10,0:20:00.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她給我看了自製的布娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛  做得很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.21,0:20:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就算是朋友了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.69,0:20:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們也是千尋的朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我去試試看和那孩子搭話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.65,0:20:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家能收下這些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾摩朗  佩夫洛  喵比利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.59,0:20:38.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋啪夫  優汪特  朵莎朵莎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  佩夫洛  到我這來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓喵也拿一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是朋友吧  來交換郵箱地址吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:20:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:20:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚  淚腺的開關又…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.23,0:21:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰  紀惠  麻音  謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  噗喲助  要再來玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「下次一定要登上黑瀧山的山頂」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.15,0:21:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家老姐發來了這樣可怕的傳言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.90,0:21:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋  謝謝你過來看我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.53,0:21:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:22:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那時聽說楓喵交到了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實覺得很寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.99,0:22:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.31,0:22:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算遠隔他鄉  時光荏苒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.18,0:22:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也一直是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.75,0:22:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在那個時候那個地方相遇的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.82,0:22:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不會消逝的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.48,0:22:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還要和今後相遇的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展開的新的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.84,0:22:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要積極向前看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.25,0:24:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集「因為是曾經的回憶」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.86,0:24:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「而且因為是某一天的回憶」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
